Interface Graph<E extends Edge<V,​I,​L>,​V extends Vertex<I>,​I,​L>

  • Type Parameters:
    E - edges
    V - vertices
    I - values inside vertices
    L - length of edges
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    GraphImpl
    public interface Graph<E extends Edge<V,​I,​L>,​V extends Vertex<I>,​I,​L>
    General graph interface. May use whatever implementation of the Edge and Vertex interfaces you like.
